Release Notes:  HRRR v4.0.4

v4.0.4 - released September 30, 2020 following the completion of a successful 30-day EMC stability test
* Final set of HRRRv4 code changes prior to operational implementation
   * Great Salt Lake temperature fix, involves WRF source code changes
   * Update GSI code for EUMETSAT BUFR format change
   * Add mass density to gempak files
   * Update BUFRLIB from version 11.0.1 to 11.3.0
   * HRRRDAS changes
      * Enhance ob qc by using the prior ensemble mean
      * Skip EnKF step when observations aren't available
      * Add a check for the completion of the perturbed boundary conditions
      * Use faster copy commands and remove a redundant copy command


